{
  "stem": "18186.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 323.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was going to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's when she wanted me to with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she-- she wanted me to be-- she wanted me to be her daughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's when I said, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we, also all the Polacks and Russian, we-- we had to also go further up, run away from the-- from the Russian army, until there was a stop, finished.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's where I was-- we were liberated, in [INAUDIBLE], or something like this, a town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germany, I'm talking about Germany now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not talking about Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, everybody had to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they didn't-- they didn't want us to be-- to be liberated with the-- with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did-- I assume they probably thought, the German people, that they're not losing the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That this is gonna come back, you know, it's just temporarily.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then it-- we know in the end what it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then-- so I said, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she left by herself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went with my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where we-- we was-- it was [NON-ENGLISH], or so, the name of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stopped there for another couple of weeks or so, maybe less.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the Russians came, and we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then the war was over?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in April.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we were-- I went back to the Polish family, back to the farm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, who was occupied already by the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we was-- stayed there for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we moved to another farm, which was close by.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a smaller farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally I started to see-- and there was-- there was at that time, was the Polish family and me, and the children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing happened to any of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
